text: Nastassia Parfenava (born 5 November 1989) is a Belarusian synchronized swimmer. She competed in the women's duet at the 2008 Olympic Games with Katsiaryna Kulpo. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Belarus Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 2008 Summer Olympics
